assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Fuji Corporation develops, sells, and imports and exports tires, wheels, and accessories for automobiles in Japan. The company also provides various parts, such as suspensions, coilovers, air suspension controllers, rod arm bars, brake pads, brake hoses, lateral lots, stabilizers, brake discs, lowering kits, shock absorbers, air valves, hub rings, wheel hooks, air sensors, center caps, rubber paints, drive recorders, radars, radar + drive recorder sets, TV-kits, engine starters, throttle controllers, digital tuning boxes, power back door kits, suspension kits, DRC coding less kits, car mats, seat covers, cushions, steering wheel covers, steering parts, scarfs, front pipes, exhaust diffusers, muffler cutters, sport seats, roof baskets, roof boxes, snow melting heaters, aero parts, rim tapes, HID headlight kits, intake parts, lenses, air cleaners, LED conversion kits, batteries, HKS oil, jacks, wrenches, puncture first aid kits, emergency rotating lights, and others. In addition, it offers furniture products. The company sells its products through stores and mail orders, as well as online. The company was incorporated in 1968 and is headquartered in Tomiya, Japan.
